{
  "uuid": "904ffd36a9f6f554cb89a613d3a6aac4",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Class 3 Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>Are you a reliable and responsible driver who enjoys being on the road and working in a supportive team environment? Kings Cart Coffee is looking for a <strong>Delivery Driver (Class 3/3A)</strong> to join our logistics team! In this role, you will play an important part in ensuring timely deliveries and supporting our warehouse operations. If you have a valid Class 3/3A driving license and enjoy hands-on work, we’d love to hear from you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform deliveries of coffee beans, machines, and event equipment to various locations.</li>\n  <li>Assist in packing, labeling, and storing items in the warehouse.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with the events and logistics team to ensure timely and accurate deliveries.</li>\n  <li>Load and unload goods, ensuring all items are transported safely and securely.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and upkeep of the company vehicle.</li>\n  <li>Assist in setup of basic equipment when required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Valid <strong>Class 3/3A driving license</strong> is a must.</li>\n  <li>Prior delivery or logistics experience is an advantage.</li>\n  <li><strong>Physically fit and able to carry items up to 30KG</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Responsible, punctual, and a team player.</li>\n  <li>Able to work flexible hours, including weekends and public holidays if needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 day work week</li>\n  <li>Staff Discount</li>\n  <li>Birthday Leave</li>\n  <li>Medical Benefits</li>\n  <li>Bi-Annual Bonus</li>\n  <li>Training and Uniform provided</li>\n  <li>Skill development and career progression opportunities</li>\n  <li>$1200 New Join Bonus Incentive (T&amp;C applies)</li>\n</ul>",
